{"word":"Hormah","slug":"hormah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hormah</b> <a href=\"#/H2767\">H2767</a> <br/> A city southwest of the Dead Sea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=45'>Num 14:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=3'>Num 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=44'>Deu 1:44</a><br/> Taken by Judah and Simeon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=17'>Jdg 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=14'>Jos 12:14</a><br/> Allotted to Simeon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=4'>Jos 19:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=30'>1Ch 4:30</a><br/> Within the territory allotted to Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=30'>Jos 15:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=30'>1Sa 30:30</a>"}]}